query:
SELECT u.id, u.email, u.name, u.role, tp.id as profile_id, tp.approvalStatus 
FROM users u 
LEFT JOIN tutor_profiles tp ON u.id = tp.userId 
WHERE u.email = 'contact-us@edkonnect.com';
